this project can ensure you do not need to compile the xposed 
project everytime when hook different function by xposed.
all you need to do is: modify the config.txt !!!


fill the config.txt,then upload config.txt to /sdcard.
adb push config.txt /sdcard/config.txt

##config.txt

package_name:
class_name:
function_name:
args_type:


[1]args_return_print_module.apk is the xposed module for print the target function args and return vale.
[2]xposed folder contain xposed framework and jar
[3]XposedHook folder contain the source code for xposed module.



